OL,3,CThe family-run Christmas pudding shop
OL,4,Cwhere business is booming
OL,6,FBusiness is booming at one dessert
OL,7,Fshop in Worcester, where their
OL,8,Ftraditional Christmas pudding recipe
OL,9,Fhas remained untouched for more than a
OL,10,Fcentury.
OL,12,FThe Halpin family's Christmas pudding
OL,13,Frecipe, created in the 1880s, is now a
OL,14,Fkey part of the 'Nana Lily's' business
OL,15,F- which keeps growing year-on-year.
OL,17,FThis year, they have sold 3,000
OL,18,Fpuddings - a 50% increase on last year.
