OL,3,CThe family-run Christmas pudding shop
OL,4,Cwhere business is booming
OL,6,FThey soon hope to employ people
OL,7,Foutside of the family, but, they say,
OL,8,Fthey won't be tempted into modern ways
OL,9,Fof baking.
OL,11,F"We still use an open steamer, we
OL,12,Fdon't use traditional baking methods
OL,13,Fof today and mass production, Elisa
OL,14,FHalpin-Barnett, the youngest member of
OL,15,Fthe team told ITV News.
OL,17,F"We keep everything the same so that
OL,18,Fthe recipe stays exactly as its meant
OL,19,Fto be", she added.
